{"tid":1511921,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【香港醒晨】G7為何撐港高舉《中英聯合聲明》？","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T16:35:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7858c084cd529dca876e4f7b31f71e152dc7fe","tid":1511921,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"【香港醒晨】G7為何撐港高舉《中英聯合聲明》？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TOtYCW9j0GQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTOtYCW9j0GQ&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=f50d0cfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TOtYCW9j0GQ</a><br />\n<br />\nRFA 自由亞洲粵語<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓︰吳明德博士（經濟時事評論員）<br />\n<br />\n在法國比亞里茨召開的七大工業國集團（G7）峰會於周一（26 日）閉幕，會後成員國發表聯合聲明，提及香港局勢。七國重申 1984 年《中英聯合聲明》的存在以及重要性，又呼籲避免使用暴力。英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）會後表示，七國「深切關注」香港局勢，支持「穩定和繁榮」的香港。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人耿爽周二（27日）回應，已多次強調香港事務純屬中國內政，任何外國政府組織和個人無權干預。他重申中方的事情，自己會處理好，請七國集團成員不要再居心叵測、多管閒事、圖謀不軌。<br />\n<br />\n香港的事情真的是純屬中國內政嗎？如果香港只是一個像上海深圳一樣的內地城市，西方國家又會否以同樣力度表示關注？「外國勢力」在香港問題上為何擁有發言權？<br />\n<br />\n本集《香港醒晨》再次請來了經濟時事評論員吳明德博士，為大家分析為何「外國勢力」如此關心香港？除了香港被形容為「廿一世紀的西柏林」之外，香港的國際地位對中國與西方發達國家意味著甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n主持︰黎加路<br />\n<br />\n（以上評論純屬主持及嘉賓個人觀點，並不代表本台立場。）<br />\n<br />\n#香港醒晨<br />\n#G7<br />\n#反送中<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台（Radio Free Asia）總部設在美國華盛頓，為言論自由受限的亞洲國家和地區提供完整而免費的新聞報道。致力以多媒體形式發送新聞，成為一個讓大眾獲得可靠消息的平台。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訂閱自由亞洲電台粵語部頻道 <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fsubscription_c...&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=c7ff2811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...</a><br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台粵語部 | RFA Cantonese <br />\n<br />\n網址：<a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/cantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=9630a8a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfa.org/cantonese</a><br />\nFacebook 臉書：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=398854b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa</a><br />\nTwitter 推特：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Rfacantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRfacantonese&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=f06c78d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Rfacantonese</a><br />\nGoogle +：<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/+CantoneseRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.google.com%2F%2BCantoneseRFA&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=c1f65cf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://plus.google.com/+CantoneseRFA</a><br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/cantoneseRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FcantoneseRFA&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=c4bd22a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/user/cantoneseRFA</a><br />\nSoundCloud: <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/rfacantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Frfacantonese&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=29f3e5f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/rfacantonese</a>"},{"pid":"ae71315c19048b6f3614fb3bc37b91a3f24d3dc0","tid":1511921,"uid":55128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZ